::Dollen::

        Dollen is about to speak to GoldenEye, when suddenly he has another
vision of the beautiful bot.  Danger........Danger again......This
time......Worse.........He put his hands on his head.

       "Ughh.....Hey, did you say Megatron?  As in the Predacon commander?
I've heard about him, I've been doing my homework!!!!!  Anyway, just take me
to wherever your base is, and I'll join your group of Predacons," He paused
and thought about the beautiful fem bot, "Umm, do you happen to know a
female bot with a beast mode of a silver fox??"
